ng paid what from the Treasury=E2=80=94=E2=80=9Csort of all that DOGE stuff=
,=E2=80=9D he said, which Wall Street types are giving =E2=80=9Ca standing =
ovation.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;"><br/>But given the largel=
