ivated the Wall Street donor class to lean so heavily into Trump last Novem=
ber, I wondered? =E2=80=9CThey don=E2=80=99t think being rich is
enough,=E2=80=9D one of my sources told me. =E2=80=9CThey think they need t=
o be <em>venerated</em> for being rich, and Biden didn=E2=80=99t venerate t=
